Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.72,0:00:18.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Brave Exkaiser
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.66,0:00:24.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Over a million of them shine with a blue light
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.96,0:00:31.01,Default,,0,0,0,,The shards of love have scattered
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.42,0:00:38.01,Default,,0,0,0,,It's brewing in this world
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.01,0:00:40.97,Default,,0,0,0,,A storm that you'll confront
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.97,0:00:44.52,Default,,0,0,0,,And because I believe in you
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.77,0:00:49.44,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not afraid of anything
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.65,0:00:53.65,Default,,0,0,0,,GO WITH ME Exkaiser
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.11,0:00:57.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Courage and friendship
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.28,0:01:03.12,Default,,0,0,0,,That moment when we join our strength GATHER WAY
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.75,0:01:06.67,Default,,0,0,0,,GO WITH ME Exkaiser
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.04,0:01:10.04,Default,,0,0,0,,I'd almost forgotten it
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.17,0:01:18.39,Default,,0,0,0,,The fiery burning and important PASSIONATE feeling in my heart
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.26,0:01:37.11,Default,,0,0,0,,This mysterious and boundless Universe...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.74,0:01:48.04,Default,,0,0,0,,It was here that the evil energy life forms, the space pirate Geisters,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.37,0:01:51.32,Default,,0,0,0,,set their sights on the treasures of humans and snuck onto Earth.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.29,0:01:59.65,Default,,0,0,0,,However, thwarting their lust for devastation, the perfect hero stands in their way.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.72,0:02:02.87,Default,,0,0,0,,He is Exkaiser of the cosmic police.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.62,0:02:06.30,Default,,0,0,0,,This is the story of the battle between good and evil that has spanned across the universe,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.63,0:02:09.89,Default,,0,0,0,,and of brave Exkaiser and his comrades.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.27,0:02:18.61,Default,,0,0,0,,The Pharmacy is Empty!?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.07,0:02:21.17,Default,,0,0,0,,"Mysterious Robot Attacks Rocket"!?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.29,0:02:22.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Idiot!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.32,0:02:25.60,Default,,0,0,0,,This isn't a grade school newspaper!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.94,0:02:27.82,Default,,0,0,0,,But chief!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.12,0:02:31.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Didn't you see them as well?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.00,0:02:32.97,Default,,0,0,0,,You blockhead!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.02,0:02:36.64,Default,,0,0,0,,I told you that unless we have a photographic proof, I don't want it in the newspaper!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.67,0:02:38.78,Default,,0,0,0,,But my camera was--
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.84,0:02:41.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Shut up! I've had it with your excuses!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.71,0:02:44.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Next time this happens, I'll take three months of your pay!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.78,0:02:48.93,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right... I'm on the short end of the stick...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.13,0:02:55.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Never give up! Scoop is my name, and scoop is my game!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.27,0:02:57.61,Default,,0,0,0,,MAGMA MAGMA MAGMA MAGMA MAGMA 
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.00,0:03:02.99,Default,,0,0,0,,And if I have these, I'll be number one in Japan!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.24,0:03:08.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Very Very Power Up!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.56,0:03:14.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Joanna...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.73,0:03:16.39,Default,,0,0,0,,I love you...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.34,0:03:20.91,Default,,0,0,0,,It's getting better...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.95,0:03:24.24,Default,,0,0,0,,-Please! Let this pass!\N-If we keep doing like this...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.86,0:03:29.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, you jerks! How long are you going to sit around!?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.13,0:03:30.02,Default,,0,0,0,,What did you say!?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.48,0:03:33.41,Default,,0,0,0,,...is what Dino Geist-sama told me to say.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.98,0:03:36.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Didn't he instruct us to gather information on this planet?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.85,0:03:40.16,Default,,0,0,0,,-Yeah, that's why we stole TVs first--hmm?\N-When you're feeling down...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.37,0:03:42.54,Default,,0,0,0,,...take Magma Drink and Power Up!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.75,0:03:43.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Very Very!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.82,0:03:44.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Power Up!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.05,0:03:46.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Very Very!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.25,0:03:48.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Gulp gulp gulp gulp gulp 
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.21,0:03:52.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Magma Power!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.67,0:03:58.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Take Magma Drink and Very Very Power Up!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.85,0:04:00.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, if we had that...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.25,0:04:02.97,Default,,0,0,0,,and we'd be Very Very Power Up!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.34,0:04:05.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Alright, let's go get it!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.62,0:04:09.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Eh!? Onee-chan caught a cold?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.19,0:04:17.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Mama, bring me more covers!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.49,0:04:20.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Really? Shouldn't you be cooling down?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.44,0:04:22.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Cool down? That's nonsense!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.62,0:04:24.78,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't help it that I'm shivering with cold!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.37,0:04:27.70,Default,,0,0,0,,I think I should call the doctor...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.88,0:04:31.76,Default,,0,0,0,,It's fine! When you catch cold, you'd better stay warm and sweat a lot,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.81,0:04:33.94,Default,,0,0,0,,and that will bring down the fever and lessen my weight, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.19,0:04:38.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Never mind that! Just bring me more covers!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.12,0:04:41.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay. Just drink up your medicine
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.86,0:04:42.72,Default,,0,0,0,,I will!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.41,0:04:52.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Only three more kilos...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.61,0:04:54.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Onee-chan, are you alright?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.88,0:05:00.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks to this, I'm skipping school and dieting at once! Two birds with one stone!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.48,0:05:02.94,Default,,0,0,0,,I wouldn't dare give up this opportunity!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.16,0:05:04.53,Default,,0,0,0,,So that's what this is about...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.10,0:05:06.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, I'm off!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.94,0:05:08.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, hold it right there.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.58,0:05:11.19,Default,,0,0,0,,You're gonna help me with my diet!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.55,0:05:13.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, pretend you're a hot-water bottle...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.95,0:05:18.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Bye!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.66,0:05:23.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on, move it! You're gonna make me late!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.74,0:05:24.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Is it not working again?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.90,0:05:27.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Kouta, can you kick it from behind?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.54,0:05:29.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe that'll help it move.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.85,0:05:34.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Papa, doing that will get you nowhere! Even cars might have feelings!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.30,0:05:37.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't worry about it! Just get in!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.57,0:05:40.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Papa doesn't mean any harm.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.24,0:05:45.25,Default,,0,0,0,,He really likes this car, so he wants you to keep up with the good job!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.94,0:05:46.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Got it?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.38,0:05:52.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Bye bye!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.36,0:05:55.93,Default,,0,0,0,,I see... Even cars have feelings...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.85,0:06:06.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Good, this is the place.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.28,0:06:07.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Alright.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.55,0:06:11.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Yamai Pharmacy
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.64,0:06:17.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Earthquake!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.91,0:06:22.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Earthquake!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.12,0:06:24.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? Nothing's shaking...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.35,0:06:32.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Thief!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.97,0:06:37.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Good morning!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.92,0:06:46.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Everyone-
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.13,0:06:52.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Class is canceled today since more than half of the class called in sick--
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.17,0:06:55.32,Default,,0,0,0,,and our class is closing down for the day.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.54,0:06:58.39,Default,,0,0,0,,So I ask you to study at home--
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.35,0:07:05.18,Default,,0,0,0,,I guess Kotomi-chan is sick, too...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.76,0:07:10.28,Default,,0,0,0,,I see it's true what they say, that the stupid never fall ill.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.75,0:07:13.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, really? And aren't you as bright as day!?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.07,0:07:17.95,Default,,0,0,0,,The cook at my estate creates nothing but A1 healthy meals.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.23,0:07:21.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Also, we have direct access to all the herbal medicines straight from the origin.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.21,0:07:23.69,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm far different from you commoners.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.66,0:07:30.10,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right, I should pay Kotomi-chan a visit!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.74,0:07:34.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh no!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.67,0:07:37.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Kotomi, hang in there!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.96,0:07:42.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Kotomi-chan! Are you alright!?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.64,0:07:43.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Kouta...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.90,0:07:46.43,Default,,0,0,0,,She suddenly fell ill with a fever.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.52,0:07:47.29,Default,,0,0,0,,A fever?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.45,0:07:48.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Please, you're in the way..
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.13,0:08:03.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Scoop... Scoop... Scoop... Scoop...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.97,0:08:09.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Tokuda-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.06,0:08:12.54,Default,,0,0,0,,What's wrong, Kouta-kun? You look down.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.00,0:08:14.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah... down...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.65,0:08:21.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, right! That drink you got! You said it would cure colds and everything, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.06,0:08:23.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, you mean that Magma Drink?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.83,0:08:25.31,Default,,0,0,0,,That's it! I could use one of those!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.80,0:08:28.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, I think you can buy them at the pharmacy over-- huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.38,0:08:36.51,Default,,0,0,0,,What was that?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.72,0:08:37.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's check it out!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.48,0:08:43.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Help me!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.34,0:08:46.87,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a scoop!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.83,0:08:54.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Power Up! Power Up!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.57,0:09:02.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, this is the editorial department of Touto Newspaper.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.70,0:09:04.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Chief! It's a scoop!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.20,0:09:06.43,Default,,0,0,0,,What in the world is going on!?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.85,0:09:07.98,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a medicine thief!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.19,0:09:09.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Moreover, they're taking the whole store!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.78,0:09:12.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Drugstores are falling down as if they're being eaten from inside!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.89,0:09:14.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Ahhhh, there goes another one!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.62,0:09:17.81,Default,,0,0,0,,This is the eighth one! Every drugstore in the vicinity is under attack!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.12,0:09:21.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Tokuda, you aren't sleepwalking again, are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.28,0:09:23.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Chief! This is a real scoop!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.70,0:09:27.03,Default,,0,0,0,,I bet some alien race fell sick and has to steal all our medicine.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.20,0:09:29.60,Default,,0,0,0,,You weren't doing your job and watched some sci-fi videos, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.76,0:09:31.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Chief! I'm not lying!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.10,0:09:35.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Moron! No human could plow through the Earth!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.58,0:09:39.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Drugstore? Something humans can't do?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.21,0:09:40.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Sounds like...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.08,0:09:46.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Well?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.95,0:09:48.13,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't feel anything...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.44,0:09:51.13,Default,,0,0,0,,It can't be! Maybe we should drink more!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.84,0:09:56.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, gimme one!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.69,0:09:59.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Screw you! I stole these.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.64,0:10:01.52,Default,,0,0,0,,I want to try one for myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.78,0:10:05.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Someone as brainless as you probably doesn't have anything to power up...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.64,0:10:06.42,Default,,0,0,0,,What!?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.60,0:10:19.29,Default,,0,0,0,,If you end up drinking all the treasures,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.36,0:10:20.80,Default,,0,0,0,,that won't get us anywhere!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.96,0:10:23.84,Default,,0,0,0,,...is what Dino Geist-sama said.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.80,0:10:35.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Dino Geist-sama has an order.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.79,0:10:37.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Take much more.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.46,0:10:40.83,Default,,0,0,0,,There must be a location where they create such things.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.24,0:10:43.64,Default,,0,0,0,,I see! And that's why he's the boss!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.13,0:10:47.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Leave this one to me...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.06,0:10:51.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Asahidai General Hospital
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.34,0:11:01.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Nurse, will Kotomi-chan be alright?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.01,0:11:07.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course! As long as she takes her medicine and gets plenty of rest, she'll be fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.68,0:11:10.40,Default,,0,0,0,,But all the drugstores in the city were attacked...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.65,0:11:13.44,Default,,0,0,0,,There's a drugstore in the hospital, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.74,0:11:14.42,Default,,0,0,0,,There is?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.95,0:11:15.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Fuuko!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.16,0:11:18.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Fuuko! Fuuko! Fuuko!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.89,0:11:20.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Fuuko! Are you alright?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.48,0:11:23.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Papa? What about your work?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.22,0:11:26.17,Default,,0,0,0,,I was told that Fuuko was brought to the hospital...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.45,0:11:30.45,Default,,0,0,0,,It's just a simple cold. Looks like she overheated herself.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.65,0:11:33.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Diet... Only 3 more kilograms...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.84,0:11:36.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Fuuko, get a hold of yourself!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.32,0:11:45.81,Default,,0,0,0,,약...약국이!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.24,0:11:48.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Eh!? This was where the medicine was!?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.25,0:11:50.49,Default,,0,0,0,,How could this happen...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.76,0:11:52.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Is there any way to replenish the medicine in storage?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.22,0:11:57.49,Default,,0,0,0,,I have no idea, but every pharmacy that supplies us hasn't re-stocked yet...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.74,0:11:59.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Eh? Then what about Kotomi-chan?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.97,0:12:17.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn those Geisters...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.29,0:12:22.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Sky Max! I'm checking out every location hit.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.18,0:12:24.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't lag behind!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.19,0:12:26.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Ha! You're one to talk!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.37,0:12:34.49,Default,,0,0,0,,This type of situation is definitely the work of the Geisters.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.24,0:12:40.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Seems they're after this "medicine" thing...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.74,0:12:42.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Every place selling that was completely wiped out.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.14,0:12:45.90,Default,,0,0,0,,So that leaves us with the source of the medicine.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.46,0:12:47.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Kouta...?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.76,0:12:53.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Exkaiser! Take me to the pharmaceutical plant!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.93,0:12:55.00,Default,,0,0,0,,To the pharmaceutical plant?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.29,0:12:57.49,Default,,0,0,0,,I have to get medicine. Please!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.11,0:12:59.33,Default,,0,0,0,,But it's dangerous.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.48,0:13:00.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Dangerous?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.48,0:13:03.42,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right. I'm sure the Geisters will attack the pharmaceutical plant.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.49,0:13:05.30,Default,,0,0,0,,You can take care of the Geisters, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.69,0:13:07.67,Default,,0,0,0,,If I don't get the medicine, Kotomi-chan might die!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.98,0:13:09.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Please, Exkaiser!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.84,0:13:11.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Exkaiser...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.21,0:13:13.99,Default,,0,0,0,,This boy knows who we are?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.44,0:13:16.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Exkaiser?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.82,0:13:18.42,Default,,0,0,0,,He is my comrade, Dash Max.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.80,0:13:19.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Hello.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.33,0:13:22.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Boy! Leave this to us!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.85,0:13:26.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Exkaiser!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.54,0:13:30.77,Default,,0,0,0,,OK, get in..
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.38,0:13:48.16,Default,,0,0,0,,From the pharmacy to the hospital...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.27,0:13:50.24,Default,,0,0,0,,I bet they'll hit the pharmaceutical plant next.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.57,0:13:52.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, what a brilliant deduction!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.69,0:13:56.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe I should become a detective instead!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.49,0:14:03.66,Default,,0,0,0,,They really came!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.46,0:14:08.66,Default,,0,0,0,,So, which one is the Very Very Power Up?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.53,0:14:11.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Screw this! We'll take 'em all!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.29,0:14:31.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Alright! Rip 'em all off!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.00,0:14:45.50,Default,,0,0,0,,This is amazing!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.70,0:14:48.57,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a scoop! It's a scoop! Scoop!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.94,0:15:00.54,Default,,0,0,0,,All the medicine is being stolen!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.92,0:15:01.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Exkaiser!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.97,0:15:04.59,Default,,0,0,0,,-All right! We know what to do!\N-Boy, leave this to us!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.81,0:15:28.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Change, Exkaiser!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.73,0:15:38.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Change, Dash Max!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.15,0:15:52.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Geisters! We Kaisers will not allow you to proceed with your evil plans!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.38,0:15:54.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn you, Exkaiser! You had to show up!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.55,0:15:58.29,Default,,0,0,0,,I have crossed the galaxy to capture all of you...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.70,0:15:59.72,Default,,0,0,0,,You won't get away!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.34,0:16:00.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Shut up!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.92,0:16:19.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't think we'll come quietly...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.42,0:16:22.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, make your move!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.21,0:16:25.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Then, here we come... Do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.73,0:16:36.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Exkaiser!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.50,0:16:41.11,Default,,0,0,0,,-Now's our chance.\N-Right!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.25,0:16:48.21,Default,,0,0,0,,No! The medicine tank!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.89,0:16:50.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Exkaiser!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.00,0:16:58.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Exkaiser!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.32,0:17:14.82,Default,,0,0,0,,What!?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.42,0:17:23.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Change, Sky Max!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.34,0:17:36.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Just a bit more for my scoop! Scoop!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.41,0:17:41.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry about that we're late!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.57,0:17:43.69,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you mean? You saved us.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.85,0:17:50.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Leave this one to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.88,0:17:53.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Right. Take care of it, Exkaiser!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.38,0:17:54.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Drill Max! Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.98,0:17:55.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Right!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.27,0:18:02.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey now! You'll fight with me!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.25,0:18:10.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Change, Drill Max!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.62,0:18:14.33,Default,,0,0,0,,The Max Team assembles!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.17,0:18:16.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Screw you all!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.60,0:18:26.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Max Team, Form Up!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.60,0:19:01.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Triple Fusion, God Max!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.98,0:19:04.34,Default,,0,0,0,,That's it! Get those Geisters!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.72,0:19:11.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah! The scoop turned into a bigger scoop!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.32,0:19:17.76,Default,,0,0,0,,All of you're going down altogether! Get them!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.93,0:19:33.70,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm next in the ring!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.05,0:19:37.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Exkaiser! Now!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.75,0:19:39.44,Default,,0,0,0,,King Loader!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.53,0:20:29.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Giant Fusion, King Exkaiser!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.04,0:20:39.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Kaiser Sword!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.49,0:21:01.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Thunder Flash!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.17,0:21:15.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Dammit!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.72,0:21:31.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Alright!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.56,0:21:36.72,Default,,0,0,0,,I finally took it! I finally got a scoop! Yay!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.68,0:21:39.40,Default,,0,0,0,,This is a rain of Magma Drink!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.92,0:21:42.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Is it pouring out for my celebration?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.70,0:21:46.02,Default,,0,0,0,,-Kouta! Hurry and get the medicine.\N-I will!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.70,0:21:57.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Doctor! Here's the medicine!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.98,0:22:00.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you! That will just do.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.09,0:22:03.63,Default,,0,0,0,,-Give this to Kotomi-chan.\N-Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.91,0:22:05.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Now everyone should be safe thanks to this.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.16,0:22:07.56,Default,,0,0,0,,You must be worried about Fuuko-san as well..
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.76,0:22:10.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, right! My sister was brought here, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.57,0:22:16.09,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't need any medicine... My diet...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.12,0:22:19.01,Default,,0,0,0,,No way! I gained!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.16,0:22:22.73,Default,,0,0,0,,I finally got a scoop!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.91,0:22:25.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Ta-da!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.76,0:22:28.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? What!? It didn't work!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.93,0:22:36.85,Default,,0,0,0,,That can't be!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.90,0:22:40.09,Default,,0,0,0,,I failed again.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.97,0:22:55.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Faraway wind carries your dream
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.97,0:23:05.07,Default,,0,0,0,,What could you discover from this excited feeling
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.78,0:23:15.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Dreams get bigger strongly and fast
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.12,0:23:22.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't forget to be who you are
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.79,0:23:31.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Embrace your enthusiastic heart
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.05,0:23:39.06,Default,,0,0,0,,And try walking that path
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.02,0:23:50.36,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm on a date with Kotomi-chan in a submarine!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.87,0:23:54.99,Default,,0,0,0,,And we're gonna see a sunken ship that's full of treasure!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.89,0:23:57.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Isn't that romantic?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.73,0:23:59.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Uwah! The Geisters again!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.61,0:24:02.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah! They're causing an undersea eruption!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.20,0:24:05.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Next on Brave Exkaiser,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.97,0:24:08.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Our Sunken Ship Expedition Party
Dialogue: 0,0:24:09.24,0:24:11.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Is there an alien in your home, too?
